{"tid":2422694,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我問過師傅啦 向華強今鋪要改名先可以轉運","createTime":"2021-02-25T11:16:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T17:17:24.000Z","uid":265783,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"82d2459569fd692c877fe0ab3abd5622c0c16605","tid":2422694,"uid":265783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:16:58.000Z","msg":"我搵<strong>師傅</strong>睇過啦<br />\n<strong>師傅</strong>中指一算話向華強今次要<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">轉運</span></span><br />\n佢兩個仔就要改一改名<br />\n<br />\n<strong>師傅話</strong><br />\n細仔叫<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">柒左</span></span><br />\n大仔叫<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"blue\">柒右</span></span><br />\n咁就年尾<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">紅</span></span>到年頭<br />\n正月初柒最旺 時曰：<span class=\"xx-large\">柒頭</span><br />\n<br />\n今年發展方向 一路向西 或者 一路向北啦<br />\n風水角度左為膠（左<span class=\"navy\">膠</span>）右為藍（右<span class=\"blue\">藍</span>）中（<span class=\"red\">華強</span>）<br />\n<br />\n宜：親中 忌：移民 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"x-large\">you welcome</span>"},{"pid":"b1d15be008f318649870b1b1be4bd4f872718b79","tid":2422694,"uid":111322,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:17:35.000Z","msg":"唔好勉強"},{"pid":"ed7e74f780b91ae8214e3bc48d463f45440d0f44","tid":2422694,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:21:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /